	*We construct the necessary variables: COICOP_2dig COICOP_3dig COICOP_4dig
	gen str6 COICOP_2dig = substr(string(product_code,"%06.0f"), 1,2) 
	gen str6 COICOP_3dig = substr(string(product_code,"%06.0f"), 1,3) 
